      • loadClassOrXml

        private static <T> T loadClassOrXml(java.lang.String asString,
                                    java.lang.Class<T> requiredType,
                                    java.lang.ClassLoader l,
                                    java.lang.String[] packageSearchPath)
                             throws java.lang.ReflectiveOperationException,
                                    TypeConverterJavaBean.FileReadException,
                                    TypeConverterJavaBean.NoTypeFoundException
        Converts an object given as a String to the original type. This tries to convert primitive types (like numbers) first. If this is not successful, asString is interpreted as a class name and loading the appropriate class is attempted (potentially prefixed with entries in packageSearchPath). If conversion is still not successful, then loading an xml file with the name asString is attempted.
        类型参数:
        T - Type of returned object.
        参数:
        asString - String representation of an object.
        requiredType - The desired target type.
        l - The class loader to use.
        packageSearchPath - A package search path.
        返回:
        The object converted/compatible with requiredType.
        抛出:
        java.lang.ReflectiveOperationException
        TypeConverterJavaBean.FileReadException
        TypeConverterJavaBean.NoTypeFoundException

      • searchAndInstanciateClass

        private static java.lang.Object searchAndInstanciateClass(java.lang.String className,
                                                          java.lang.ClassLoader l,
                                                          java.lang.String[] searchPath)
                                                   throws java.lang.ReflectiveOperationException,
                                                          java.lang.IllegalAccessException
        Load an instantiate a class using classloader l. If a class className is not found, it is searched for in the package search path.

        If, e.g., className is "MultipleReplicationExperiment" and the package search path searchPath contains an entry "jasima.core.experiment" , then the class jasima.core.experiment.MultipleReplicationExperiment will be looked up and instantiated.

        If no matching class could be found, null will be returned.

        抛出:
        java.lang.ReflectiveOperationException
        java.lang.IllegalAccessException

      • loadXmlFile

        private static java.lang.Object loadXmlFile(java.lang.String fileName)
                                     throws TypeConverterJavaBean.FileReadException
        Attempts to load an object from a xml-file fileName. If such a file does not exist or is not readable, null will be returned.
        抛出:
        TypeConverterJavaBean.FileReadException
        另请参阅:
        XmlUtil.loadXML(File)
